{"tid":1300782,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論]香港既核心價值","createTime":"2019-07-09T12:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T12:52:12.000Z","uid":109138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d14519b6d6d3567b97e24bf2245edb38418088d4","tid":1300782,"uid":109138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:49:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">細佬第一次出POST，有講錯請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個月發左好多個夢，令小弟對香港呢個地方既身份認同歸屬感加深左好多，眼見而家香港人既團結、互相幫助令我十分感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同時間我不斷諗香港既核心價值應該係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？我認為係自由、民主、人權、包容。而我認為呢樣野係可以大家一齊去諗同討論，接受唔同既意見，因為大家都係同一目標就係想香港變得更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以希望大家可以討論同交流一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開呢個POST最主要目的係希望大家可以討論下呢樣野，同享受我地應有既言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為我認為有改變先會進步。當然今時今日講呢D好似有小小言之過早，因為大家都打緊一場仗，我相信係一場持久戰，同時我亦相信我地會勝利。最後想講既係，兄弟爬山，各自努力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"6cffd1b431283a7627eb7a06a464bb4b36c42c28","tid":1300782,"uid":23189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:51:21.000Z","msg":"點解要用紫色字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎入去討論<br />\n<br />\n「長文慎入」勇武又好、和理非又好，自己香港自己救！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299934</a>"},{"pid":"db329cf9cea86ba4faba30f77b6895991c409fda","tid":1300782,"uid":109138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cffd1b431283a7627eb7a06a464bb4b36c42c28","tid":1300782,"uid":23189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:51:21.000Z","msg":"點解